            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)09日09:39上漲6.9元，股價漲停報76.2元，委買9,029張，成交32,145張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為電解銅箔之製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲4.68%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲4.78%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-299 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-435 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+136 張</li> <li>融資增減：-404 張</li> <li>融券增減：-164 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
